    <div class="summary">        
        <h3><a href="/questions/19460828/how-does-mongoid-know-the-difference-between-string-values-and-symbol-values" class="question-hyperlink">How does Mongoid know the difference between string values and symbol values?</a></h3>
        <div class="excerpt">
            Consider this example:

&gt; x = User.first # or any persisted Mongoid::Document
=&gt; #&lt;User _id: 52014532a6356d1ac9000001, ...&gt;
&gt; x.set :foo, :bar
=&gt; :bar
&gt; x.set :foo2, 'bar'
=&gt; ...
        </div>
             
